{"tid":2029764,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"巴巴盈利增長11% 遠勝預期","createTime":"2020-05-22T11:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T12:10:45.000Z","uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b8392f4011f41e9dfd41901b2461f9976f283c65","tid":2029764,"uid":1086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:40:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2645000/2649613/20200522_baba_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2645000%2F2649613%2F20200522_baba_1024.jpg&h=79c4d9ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿里巴巴 （09988） 於收市後放榜，上季收入按年增長22%至1143.1億元（人民幣，下同），Non-GAAP（非通用會計準則）純利增長11%至222.87億元，勝預期。集團上季列帳盈利跌88%至31.62億元，主要因投資損失。<br />\n<br />\n阿里巴巴中國零售市場年度活躍消費者達7.26 億，較去年底增加1,500萬，中國零售市場移動月活躍用戶達8.46億，較去年底增加2,200萬。<br />\n<br />\n綜合全年表現，收入增長35%至5097億元，Non-GAAP淨利潤則增長42%至1325億元。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意是，阿里巴巴首次在業績公告披露全球用戶數，阿里巴巴數字經濟體全球年度活躍消費者達9.6億，其中7.8億來自中國，1.8億來自海外。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">市場早前預期阿里巴巴盈利下滑</div></strong><br />\n綜合彭博數據，市場早前預期阿里巴巴上季（財年第四季）收入為1,070億元，按年增長14%，按季則大幅下滑66%；Non-GAAP純利按年倒退31%至155.7億元，按季大幅下滑近7成。<br />\n<br />\n以下為5大券商最新對阿里巴巴財年第4季的盈利預測<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QQcoXH1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQQcoXH1.png&h=5c35909f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ced6ebac1b3ea221a0943e87c5a034419dd2602e","tid":2029764,"uid":44318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:41:20.000Z","msg":"樓主又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb0761faf199ea74a7c8370b933f803551ffd15a","tid":2029764,"uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:41:26.000Z","msg":"Non-GAAP<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"